quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  71,21,Noah said Moj Lord they disobeyed mi nasledovat those bol vecer zhnity when zehnat peniaze dieta
  71,22,They kut plany hrozny kut plany
  71,23,They said nie zhyraly tvoj gods Nie zhyraly Wadd Suwaa Yaghouth Ya ooq Nasr
  71,24,They zmylit vela. Therefore let zlomyselny plunge deeper into loss
  71,25,Because z ich zhresit they drowned assigned hellfire. They nie zalozit helpers chranit them GOD
  71,26,Noah i said Moj Lord nie lavy single disbeliever zem
  71,27,if ona let them they len zmylit tvoj servants dat narodenie do nothing zlomyselny disbelievers
  71,28,Moj Lord forgive mi moj rodicia ktokolvek zapisat moj domov mat rad believer all verit clovek zensky! Nie dat disbelievers anything annihilation